fm: vector<int> findOriginalArray(vector<int>& changed)      {                 int n = changed.size();         if (n%2!=0) return {};                  multiset<int>Set(changed.begin(), changed.end());         vector<int>rets;         for (int t=0; t<n/2; t++)         {             int mx = *prev(Set.end());             if (mx%2!=0)                 return {};             if (Set.find(mx/2)==Set.end())                 return {};             Set.erase(Set.lower_bound(mx));             Set.erase(Set.lower_bound(mx/2));             rets.push_back(mx/2);         }         return rets;     }
